# StackSolutions - Professional Development Agency Website

## Project Overview
A modern, client-centric website for StackSolutions - a professional software development agency specializing in full-stack web development, Flutter mobile apps, digital transformation, AI automation, and SEO optimization.

## Technology Stack
- **Framework**: Next.js 14 (App Router)
- **Styling**: Tailwind CSS
- **Animations**: Framer Motion
- **Icons**: Lucide React
- **Forms**: React Hook Form + Zod validation
- **Deployment**: Vercel (recommended)

